title: Talks Machina: Discussing C1E75 - Where The Cards Fall
description: On this first episode of Talks Machina, Brian W. Foster sits down with Critical Role GM Matt Mercer to talk the previous encounters on Critical Role, answers questions from #AskTalksMachina with some of the cast, and more!
